# Certifications & Training

This directory contains verifiable records for my water utility operations licensure and continuing education, alongside my academic and practical training in Information Technology (IT) and Operational Technology (OT/ICS) cybersecurity.

### File Organization & Naming Convention
To maintain a chronological audit trail, files are stored flat in this directory using the following naming standard:
`YYYY-MM-DD_short-course-name.pdf` (e.g., `2026-06-17_210W-01-ics-deployments.pdf`).

